Number 7:

00:02:34.260 --> 00:02:37.190
social media usage increases depression and loneliness

00:02:38.340 --> 00:02:42.799
Huntail found that this was especially true of people who were already depressed

00:02:43.709 --> 00:02:50.179
It seems this is a case due to social comparison- comparing your lives to other's lives as seen on social media

00:02:51.000 --> 00:02:53.209
So if you find yourself feeling lonely or depressed

00:02:53.940 --> 00:02:57.169
Spending a bit less time on social media might be a good idea

